WEBVTT

00:05:00.042 --> 00:05:03.226
Technology alone
will not solve climate change,

00:05:03.250 --> 00:05:06.184
nor will it make air pollution
disappear overnight.

00:05:06.208 --> 00:05:10.518
But it can make the quality
of our air much more transparent,

00:05:10.542 --> 00:05:11.976
and if we can empower people

00:05:12.000 --> 00:05:14.143
to take action
to improve their own health,

00:05:14.167 --> 00:05:17.750
then together we can act
to bring an end to our pollution.

00:05:18.375 --> 00:05:19.643
Thank you very much.

00:05:19.667 --> 00:05:21.750
(Applause)